== Description ==

The '''Item Magnet''' is a type of battle item. It temporarily increases the player's chance of gaining an extra item by 50% for 30 seconds.

== Details ==

+50% Chance of gaining an extra item from [[Dungeons|Dungeon]] chests, and increases the chance of getting an item from Pokémon that drop [[Rare Hold Items]].

